{"tid":501919,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《幽遊白書全新動畫製作決定》林保全將擔任飛影配音","createTime":"2017-12-17T11:05:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-17T11:28:59.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e6b5c18ad4dc1bee767536422d31c18df3009ec3","tid":501919,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:05:14.000Z","msg":"《幽遊白書全新動畫製作決定》雖然很值得開心...但是獵人呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/190211_6789ef51348e0bcf3873c90890d9113a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F190211_6789ef51348e0bcf3873c90890d9113a.jpg&h=e9576305&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《幽遊白書全新動畫製作決定》雖然很值得開心...但是獵人圖片1<br />\n<br />\n圖片來自：<br />\n讓人興奮的不得了的消息啊！昨天看到的時候真的瘋狂的傳訊息給朋友《幽遊白書全新動畫製作決定》了啊！！！還有不少朋友不可置信的說「什麼！」今年是《幽遊白書》動畫開播的25週年紀念，不但啟動了紀念官方網站（真斂財）也發售了許多紀念週邊呢！而這次的「ジャンプフェスタ2018」Jump Festa2018 活動中也公布了新消息～～～<br />\n<br />\n原汁原味的內容在這裡<br />\n「ジャンプフェスタ2018」Jump Festa 2018<br />\n<br />\nJump Festa是雜誌週刊少年Jump、V-Jump、Jump Square（至2007年Jump Festa前是月刊少年Jump）舉辦的活動，所以這裡也聚集了很多大家所熟悉的作品，許多周邊發售也會從這場活動中公開！今年的開展為12月16日～17日<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/17/190308_0ba50d42f6e359252a30e5bff8191734.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F17%2F190308_0ba50d42f6e359252a30e5bff8191734.jpg&h=d4af394e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《幽遊白書全新動畫製作決定》雖然很值得開心...但是獵人呢- 圖片2<br />\n<br />\n圖片來自：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/tkg_movie/status/941912094911238144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftkg_movie%2Fstatus%2F941912094911238144&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3glzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=b56e4102\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Ftkg_movie%2Fstatus%2F941912094911238144&h=55aaec17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/tkg_movie/status/941912094911238144</a><br />\n而這次幽遊白書也參展了呢！<br />\n<br />\n1990年代中《七龍珠》《灌籃高手》以及《幽遊白書》可是Jump的三大代表漫畫呢！當時的漫畫銷售量非常的可觀，截至2012年時的紀錄就有4900萬冊呢！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而在這次的展出中，幽遊白書也公開了全新動畫製作決定<br />\n<br />\n由於幽遊白書動畫新作製作的相關情報太少，無法得知冨樫義博是否有參與（不然真的很想問問獵人呢Q_Q）包含聲優情報以及劇情皆是未知，但應該會是原班人馬吧！！！<br />\n目前所知道的是！官方在這次活動中宣布了將發售25週年紀念BD，而完全新作的幽遊白書動畫會收錄在裡面！不過收錄在BD裡面應該只是個小短篇吧..（不負責亂猜）"},{"pid":"ab02187e7721fc5fefc36501cf910aa2128d8c03","tid":501919,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1536330?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=kakalopo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1536330%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dkakalopo&d=rgQ2oB%2B6oMbIQfighRH3glzEg0sy7MJ6GkP0ogsbSqo%3D&h=e787f6ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1536330?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=kakalopo</a>"},{"pid":"5514f2920ab5c0be94aff20ab0f7e369b04d3373","tid":501919,"uid":29804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:15:36.000Z","msg":"點配"},{"pid":"149b721a2057dd3baf24be055401ba0197e54b1e","tid":501919,"uid":53687,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:23:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">林保全將擔任飛影配音</span><br />\n<br />\n戇鳩當有趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b1463e31e532113b676c736869c043eccc6eae","tid":501919,"uid":12690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"當年無線星期六晚第一次播 ⋯最後果兩集錄影帶仲係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  之後佢就播抵死泰山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9055d44f402bd2571142211f83ff107bf2e6251e","tid":501919,"uid":35668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T11:28:59.000Z","msg":"即係飛影唔會出場??<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}